"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-australia-news-melbourne-radio-host-suggests-new-national-flag-design-based-on-a-quintessential-symbol-of-australia-citing-paris-olympics-confusion-news-story-13975f9ef04987a5408d394b71f2c3a4\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Melbourne radio host has proposed changing the national flag to feature a \\\"quintessential symbol of Australia\\\", citing confusion arising on social media during the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9475804215393344, \"rank\": 0.05455809511896677, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 102, \"end\": 111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9701977993334598, \"rank\": 0.0274703247962162, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Melbourne radio host has suggested a new national flag design based on a \\\"quintessential symbol of Australian\\\".\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 185, \"end\": 194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9475804215393344, \"rank\": 0.05455809511896677, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9043544072511188, \"rank\": 0.08046960711836841, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"3AW Mornings host Tom Elliott said he did not mind the Australian flag as it was, but there was a lot of \\\"confusion\\\" which had arisen on social media during coverage of the Paris Olympics about why the colours of the Australian flag differed from our national sporting colours.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Elliott_(politician)\", \"score\": 0.6055751378934913, \"rank\": 0.4561403508771875, \"text\": \"Tom Elliott\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Elliott_(politician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Elliott_(politician)\"}, {\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Why do we have a red, white and blue flag, and yet our national colours are green and gold,\\\" Elliott asked.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Elliott\", \"score\": 0.9675856365381578, \"rank\": 0.01903464585615815, \"text\": \"Elliott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Elliott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Elliott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Melbourne radio host said it raised the question of whether the Australian flag should be changed before he proposed a design based on the symbol of a Kangaroo.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9475804215393344, \"rank\": 0.05455809511896677, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The kangaroo is the quintessential symbol of Australia,\\\" he said  \\\"If you wanted to unite our sporting colours of green and gold, I reckon a flag that would make sense would be a green background with the yellow kangaroo in the centre.\\\"\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9701977993334598, \"rank\": 0.0274703247962162, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Melbourne radio host pointed out\\u00a0 the famous green and gold boxing kangaroo flag was flown during Australia's historic victory in the America's Cup.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"score\": 0.9475804215393344, \"rank\": 0.05455809511896677, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1194, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9701977993334598, \"rank\": 0.0274703247962162, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now I am not saying we have the boxing kangaroo as our official national symbol,\\\" Elliott said.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Elliott\", \"score\": 0.9675856365381578, \"rank\": 0.01903464585615815, \"text\": \"Elliott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Elliott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bill_Elliott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But a stylized kangaroo - you know, like the Qantas one, but without the wings - in gold on a green background.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That could work.\\\"\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 3AW host acknowledged Australia wasn't the only country whose sporting colours differ from their national flag - with Italy and New Zealand being two other examples.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9701977993334598, \"rank\": 0.0274703247962162, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.887136516490634, \"rank\": 0.12576507766557782, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1608, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_netball_team\", \"score\": 0.6661411331167392, \"rank\": 0.26256234982639465, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_netball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_netball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the Italian flag being green, white and red, Italian sporting teams play in blue uniforms, with the national football team is nicknamed the Azzurri - which literally translates to the Blues.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1659, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Italy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Italian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9997712947817535, \"rank\": 0.00022016076365530854, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly, New Zealand's sporting colours are black with a touch of white, despite the country's national flag being similar to Australia's.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_netball_team\", \"score\": 0.6661411331167392, \"rank\": 0.26256234982639465, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_netball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_netball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9701977993334598, \"rank\": 0.0274703247962162, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand held a three-stage referendum on whether to change its national flag in 2015 and 2016.\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 2000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_netball_team\", \"score\": 0.6661411331167392, \"rank\": 0.26256234982639465, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_netball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_netball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first stage involved voters selecting between five alternative designs, with the top two moving to a second vote.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The winning design was a black and blue design with a white fern on the left and a red southern cross on the right.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But in the final stage of the referendum, this new national flag was supported by just over 43 per cent of voters.\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was compared to more than 56 per cent of New Zealanders who voted to retain the existing national flag.\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2485, \"end\": 2499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.962755833691077, \"rank\": 0.03848683670394367, \"text\": \"New Zealanders\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2010 a national poll of 652 Australians aged 14 and above found\\u00a0 66 per cent supported retaining Australia's existing national flag compared to 29 per cent who support changing the flag.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2649, \"end\": 2658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9701977993334598, \"rank\": 0.0274703247962162, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": []}]}"